name: Clock Tik Tik
author: Blitz Mobile Apps

sections.description:
With this plugin you can now easily customize WooCommerce My Account Page and add custom options related to your Pages.

WooCommerce User Dashboard or My Account page comes with minimum options, where users can review their dashboard, orders, downloads, addresses and account details. Using this plugin will allow you to create unlimited options on your My Account page without any customization.

Plugin Features

  • Unlimited number of Menu
  • Use custom pages
  • Or anything else
sections.installation:
• Upload to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory. Or Directly upload from your Plugin management page.
  • Activate the plugin through the Admin menu in WordPress
